name: Starlight Engine
background: A damage-type W-Engine made of special Ether materials. When its operator is attacked, it builds up energy and boosts its damage output. Although it does not grant the operator the power to transform into a Starlight Knight, it provides a surge of courage when the operator is in dire situations.
skill: Launching a Dodge Counter or Quick Assist increases the equipper's ATK by 12%/13.8%/15.6%/17.4%/19.2% for 12s.
